 <span data-ttu-id="fa120-123"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedAudio.StartTime%2A>属性识别操作开始时获取系统时间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fa120-123">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedAudio.StartTime%2A> property gets the system time at the start of the recognition operation.</span></span>  
  
   
  
